section.section:
The outline of coverage shall include:
a description of the principal benefits and coverage provided in the Medicare supplement policy;
a statement of the exceptions, reductions, and limitations contained in the Medicare supplement policy;
a statement of the renewal provisions, including any reservation by the carrier of a right to change premiums;
disclosure of the existence of any automatic renewal premium increases based on the policyholder's age; and
a statement that the outline of coverage is a summary of the Medicare supplement policy that is issued or applied for and that the Medicare supplement policy should be consulted to determine governing contractual provisions.
